s the record lacks airport-by-airport proof of complete suspension at"},"partialArgs":"{\"tool\": \"aar_submit_council_vote\", \"args\": \"{\\\"vote\\\":\\\"not_demonstrated\\\",\\\"rationale\\\":\\\"The raw NOTAM A1010/26 (ev_2e5195da64cb) is classified as airport-operations, closing airports in the west part of Tehran FIR except 8 daylight/CAA-permission airports, which does not establish a broad commercial airspace-region closure under the market rule. The separate two-airport complete-suspension path is not proven as the record lacks airport-by-airport proof of complete suspension at ","streamIndex":0}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"qwen/qwen3.5-plus-02-15","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782824186974,"responseId":"gen-1782824187-8ZuZwjSQsDN3AL5ygKjK","responseModel":"qwen/qwen3.5-plus-20260216"}}
